decks.notes: This deck focuses on disrupting your opponent's game plan while applying pressure with efficient creatures. It utilizes cards like Thoughtseize and Fatal Push to control the board early on, while Ephemerate and Flickerwisp provide extra value by blinking key creatures. Aether Vial allows for cheating creatures into play at instant speed. The deck aims to tax your opponent's resources with cards like White Orchid Phantom and Recruiter of the Guard, while finishing the game quickly with powerful creatures like Overlord of the Balemurk and Emperor of Bones.
